{"tid":298144,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"連登仔攝台ig tag討論區","createTime":"2017-06-26T05:13:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-28T18:55:49.000Z","uid":26845,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"24bb6d6e80d3dff1666e1194aa41b1d75fc2b235","tid":298144,"uid":26845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T05:13:09.000Z","msg":"是咁的 近排有位巴打建議玩開ig既攝台連仔一齊用個ig hashtag<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n暫時仲未有共識 希望有興趣既巴打一齊討論 <br />\n一個hashtag好唔好用都係睇大家支唔支持 所以太多人負皮反對我諗都可以收工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n暫時既hashtag提議有:<br />\n#連登攝影台<br />\n#lihkg<br />\n#我愛連登<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"429eef133f37622455744885758ee268a027e3db","tid":298144,"uid":14625,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T05:55:53.000Z","msg":"tag完都唔會有膠流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2a94b5eca3bd464d3c56101fee82ebe91717306","tid":298144,"uid":30895,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T08:43:33.000Z","msg":"打都唔識打出嚟喎"},{"pid":"ab83011f0ac3413ae0281360fb658cf401673428","tid":298144,"uid":14885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T10:11:25.000Z","msg":"互粉不掉讚？"},{"pid":"a01edf9c69f7e049a16ce73346c0f552e0dfaeeb","tid":298144,"uid":21385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T15:20:35.000Z","msg":"就咁睇個tag唔會有持久力<br />\n想普及又高質點都需要有人管理個tag先得"},{"pid":"4c3f575f9ddb5cecacca823b822304d2a938e52e","tid":298144,"uid":40672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T17:30:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>就咁睇個tag唔會有持久力<br />\n想普及又高質點都需要有人管理個tag先得</blockquote><br />\nwhich無咩可能喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92078d0e9c5afac778904a11dbd8953c7545f917","tid":298144,"uid":159